<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>some.pics (中文)</title><link>https://some.pics</link><description>只是网上的一些图片。</description><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:46:24 +0000</lastBuildDate><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3dafbd384f5</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这幅位于道格拉斯剧院旁的壁画，由洛杉矶艺术家汉娜·韦布为2024年梅肯壁画节创作。作品描绘了一只栖息在马丁·路德·金停车楼上的大蓝鹭——这种鸟类原产于梅肯。从城市天际线一英里多外的地方都能清晰望见。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Colorful mural of a stylized heron on a parking garage wall. The geometric design and cool hues of blue and purple create a bold, artistic effect." height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3dafbd384f5.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:46:24 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>时隔一年重返图书馆</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3daf4fba884</link><description>&lt;p&gt;今天去了图书馆，这是超过一年来第一次。以前我几乎每周都去，但不知怎么地，就没了这个习惯。我也不确定为什么。只是很高兴终于能再次前往。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt='A hand holds the book "Sketchbook for the Artist" by Sarah Simblet, featuring a grey circle on the cover, against a backdrop of comic books on a library shelf.' height="4032" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3daf4fba884.jpg" width="3024"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:44:35 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>金鱼素描与公共图库</title><link>https://some.pics/6a3dae8dd3e72</link><description>&lt;p&gt;我最近画了更多素描。今天用公共领域图片档案库找到的一张参考图，画了这条金鱼。这个网站对艺术家来说是个很棒的资源，精心整理了超过一万张不受版权限制的历史图片，可以自由浏览和重复使用。如果你正发愁找不到东西画，用无限浏览模式逛逛这个网站，很快就会找到吸引你目光并激发灵感的内容。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Illustration of a goldfish with large fins and speckled scales in a sketchbook, accompanied by two black Micron pens on the left. The tone is artistic." height="3024" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/dhester/6a3dae8dd3e72.jpg" width="4032"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://dhester.some.pics"&gt;@dhester&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 22:41:21 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3d50ebca8f9</link><description>&lt;p&gt;🔥 🥵 这儿真凉快&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="🔥 🥵 Frisjes hier" height="1920" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/simondh/6a3d50ebca8f9.jpg" width="1080"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://simondh.some.pics"&gt;@simondh&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 16:01:50 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title/><link>https://some.pics/6a3d4336acf48</link><description>&lt;p&gt;待办事项&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Ice cubes in a white mold, with a light blue lid next to it. " height="2000" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.some.pics/z428/6a3d4336acf48.jpg" width="1126"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Shared by &lt;a href="https://z428.some.pics"&gt;@z428&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Jun 2026 15:03:21 +0000</pubDate></item></channel></rss>